1.0.0.name: wordpress/blunt-ga
1.0.0.description:
This plugin installs Google Analytics (GA). It can be used to set up event tracking of document, file, email, click to call and outbound links. Form submission event tracking can be set up. Event tracking can be added to all conversion pages. Cross Site tracking and linking can also be set up. Tracking can be set up to track clicks as either events or as virtual page views.

The main advantages of this plugin are: * All events can be managed and viewed seperately in Google Analytics * All events can be sent as virtual page views * Conversion events directly to you analytics page reports * Ability to set up Cross Site Tracking and Linking * Ability to set up a prefix to add for page views

If you need help setting this plugin up for use in Cross Site Tracking or you have any problems setting it up and getting it working, please submit a Support Request.
